<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>77</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khi tuukhal nih zantim ah khan, Vancungmi hlasak thawng kha an theih,
 A bia thawngin an i lawm ko, Vancungmi nih hi hla kha an sak.

[C1]
   A lianngan bik Bawi si ko seh! Vawlei ah remnak bia thang ko seh, A
   zungzal in thang ko cang seh, Vawlei mi i lawm ko u.

[V2]
 Tuukhal mi nih lianhnak an hmuh, Ngai tuah u, ceunak thawngtha a si,
 Khuk bil in a kut kha an tlaih, A tha bik hla nih khan a zelh ko.

[C2]
   A lianngan bik Bawi si ko seh! Vawlei ah remnak bia thang ko seh, A
   zungzal in thang ko cang seh, Vawlei mi i lawm ko u.

[V3]
 Mikhamhtu Pathian thimmi kha, Kan leiba kha cham awk ah a ra; Retheih
 sifah ngaihchiatnak he, Kannih sualnak kha a kan tlanh cang.

[C3]
   A lianngan bik Bawi si ko seh! Vawlei ah remnak bia thang ko seh, A
   zungzal in thang ko cang seh, Vawlei mi i lawm ko u.</lyrics>
<title>VANCUNGMI HLA CH77</title>
</song>